<lb n="0865c17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0865c18" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 143 [Nos. 125(51.9), 141-142]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0865c19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>玉耶經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0865c20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0865c21" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉<note n="0865003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】</note><note n="0865003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏【大】，西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865003"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0865c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0865c2201">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT02p0865c2204" rend="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，佛
<lb n="0865c23" ed="T"/>為四輩弟子說法。時給孤獨家，先為子娶婦
<lb n="0865c24" ed="T"/><note n="0865004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（得）＋長【三】</note><note n="0865004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">長【大】，得長【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865004"><lem wit="【大】">長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">得長</rdg></app>者家女，女名玉耶，端正姝好而生憍慢，
<lb n="0865c25" ed="T"/>不以婦禮承事<note n="0865005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妐＝翁【宋】，公【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0865005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妐【大】＊，翁【宋】，公【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0865005"><lem wit="【大】">妐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">翁</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">公</rdg></app>姑夫婿。給孤長者夫妻議
<lb n="0865c26" ed="T"/>言：「子婦不順不<note n="0865006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">依＝從【三】</note><note n="0865006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">依【大】，從【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865006"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">從</rdg></app>法禮，設加杖捶不欲行
<lb n="0865c27" ed="T"/>此，置不教<note n="0865c2701" resp="CBETA" type="add">呵【CB】【麗-CB】，訶【大】</note><app n="0865c2701"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">呵<note type="cf1">K19n0771_p0795b09</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">訶</rdg></app>其過轉增，當如之何？」長者<note n="0865007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰唯＝惟曰【宋】</note><note n="0865007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰唯【大】，惟曰【宋】</note><app n="0865007"><lem wit="【大】">曰：
<lb n="0865c28" ed="T"/>「唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">惟曰</rdg></app>佛大聖善能化物，<note n="0865008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一切）＋剛【三】</note><note n="0865008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">剛【大】，一切剛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865008"><lem wit="【大】">剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">一切剛</rdg></app>強弭伏無敢不從，請
<lb n="0865c29" ed="T"/>佛來化。」妻言：「大善。」明<note n="0865009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旦＝早【三】</note><note n="0865009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">旦【大】，早【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865009"><lem wit="【大】">旦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">早</rdg></app>嚴服往詣佛所，頭
<pb n="0866a" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0143.0866a"/>
<lb n="0866a01" ed="T"/>面著地前白佛言：「我家為子娶婦甚大憍慢，
<lb n="0866a02" ed="T"/>不以<note n="0866001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮節＝婦禮【三】</note><note n="0866001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮節【大】，婦禮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866001"><lem wit="【大】">禮節</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婦禮</rdg></app>承事我子，唯願世尊，明日自屈，
<lb n="0866a03" ed="T"/>將諸弟子到舍中飯，并為玉耶說法，令心開
<lb n="0866a04" ed="T"/>解改過行善。」佛告長者：「善哉！善哉！」給孤長者
<lb n="0866a05" ed="T"/>聞佛受請，歡喜禮佛<note n="0866002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">接＝犍【宋】</note><note n="0866002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">接【大】，犍【宋】</note><app n="0866002"><lem wit="【大】">接</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">犍</rdg></app>足而去，歸舍齋戒供
<lb n="0866a06" ed="T"/>辦中飯。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866a0604" rend="inline">明日佛與千二百五十弟子到長者家，
<lb n="0866a07" ed="T"/>長者歡喜<note n="0866003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迎＝近【三】</note><note n="0866003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迎【大】，近【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866003"><lem wit="【大】">迎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">近</rdg></app>佛作禮，佛坐已定，大小皆出禮
<lb n="0866a08" ed="T"/>佛却住，玉耶逃藏不肯禮佛。佛即變化，令長
<lb n="0866a09" ed="T"/>者家，屋宅牆壁，皆如琉璃、水精之色內外相
<lb n="0866a10" ed="T"/><note n="0866004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝照【明】</note><note n="0866004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，照【明】</note><app n="0866004"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">照</rdg></app>，玉耶<note n="0866005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔見〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0866005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0866005"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛有三十二相、八十種好，身<note n="0866006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紫金色＝色紫金【宋】</note><note n="0866006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">紫金色【大】，色紫金【宋】</note><app n="0866006"><lem wit="【大】">紫
<lb n="0866a11" ed="T"/>金色</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">色紫金</rdg></app>，光明<note n="0866007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暉暉＝煒煒【三】</note><note n="0866007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暉暉【大】，煒煒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866007"><lem wit="【大】">暉暉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">煒煒</rdg></app>，玉耶惶怖心驚毛竪，即出禮
<lb n="0866a12" ed="T"/>佛，頭頂懺悔却<note n="0866008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝住【三】</note><note n="0866008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，住【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866008"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">住</rdg></app>右面。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866a1210" rend="inline">佛告玉耶：「女人不當
<lb n="0866a13" ed="T"/>自恃端正輕慢夫婿。何謂端正？除<note n="0866009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">却＝去【三】</note><note n="0866009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">却【大】，去【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866009"><lem wit="【大】">却</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">去</rdg></app>邪態八
<lb n="0866a14" ed="T"/>十四<note n="0866010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姤＝垢【三】</note><note n="0866010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姤【大】，垢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866010"><lem wit="【大】">姤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">垢</rdg></app>，定意一心是為端正，不以顏色面目
<lb n="0866a15" ed="T"/>髮綵為端正也。女人身中有十惡事，何等為
<lb n="0866a16" ed="T"/>十？一者、女人初生墮地父母不喜。二者、養育
<lb n="0866a17" ed="T"/>視無滋味。三者、女人心常畏人。四者、父母恒
<lb n="0866a18" ed="T"/>憂嫁娶。五者、與父母生相離別。六者、常畏<note n="0866011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝失【明】</note><note n="0866011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夫【大】，失【明】</note><app n="0866011"><lem wit="【大】">夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">失</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866a19" ed="T"/>婿視其顏色，歡悅輒喜瞋恚則懼。七者、懷妊
<lb n="0866a20" ed="T"/>產生甚難。八者、女人小為父母所撿錄。九者、
<lb n="0866a21" ed="T"/>中為夫婿<note n="0866012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝禁【三】</note><note n="0866012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，禁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866012"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">禁</rdg></app>制。十者、年老為兒孫所呵，從生
<lb n="0866a22" ed="T"/>至終不得自在。是為十事，女人不自覺知。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866a2217" rend="inline">玉
<lb n="0866a23" ed="T"/>耶長跪叉手白佛：「稟受<note n="0866013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賤身＝下賤【三】</note><note n="0866013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賤身【大】，下賤【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866013"><lem wit="【大】">賤身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">下賤</rdg></app>不<note n="0866014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閑＝知【三】</note><note n="0866014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閑【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866014"><lem wit="【大】">閑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">知</rdg></app>禮儀。唯
<lb n="0866a24" ed="T"/>願世尊，具說教訓為婦之法。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866a2412" rend="inline">佛告玉耶：「婦事
<lb n="0866a25" ed="T"/><note n="0866015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姑妐＝翁姑【宋】，公姑【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0866015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姑妐【大】＊，翁姑【宋】，公姑【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0866015"><lem wit="【大】">姑妐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">翁姑</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">公姑</rdg></app>夫婿，有五善三惡。何等為五善？一者、
<lb n="0866a26" ed="T"/>為婦當<note n="0866016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晚＝後【三】</note><note n="0866016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晚【大】，後【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866016"><lem wit="【大】">晚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">後</rdg></app>臥早起，櫛梳髮綵整頓衣服，洗拭
<lb n="0866a27" ed="T"/>面目勿有垢穢，執於作事先啟所尊，心常恭
<lb n="0866a28" ed="T"/>順，設有甘美不得先食。二者、夫壻呵罵不得
<lb n="0866a29" ed="T"/>瞋恨。三者、一心守夫婿，不得念邪婬。四者、常
<pb n="0866b" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0143.0866b"/>
<lb n="0866b01" ed="T"/>願夫婿長壽，出行婦當整頓家中。五者、常念
<lb n="0866b02" ed="T"/>夫善不<note n="0866017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念夫＝得念【三】</note><note n="0866017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念夫【大】，得念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866017"><lem wit="【大】">念夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">得念</rdg></app>惡，是為五善。何等為三惡？一
<lb n="0866b03" ed="T"/>者、不以婦禮承事<app type="star" corresp="#0866015"><lem wit="【大】">姑妐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">公姑</rdg></app>夫婿，但欲美食先
<lb n="0866b04" ed="T"/><note n="0866018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝取【三】</note><note n="0866018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而【大】，取【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866018"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">取</rdg></app>噉之，未冥早臥日出不起，夫<note n="0866019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲教呵＝若訶教【三】</note><note n="0866019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲教呵【大】，若訶教【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866019"><lem wit="【大】">欲教呵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">若訶教</rdg></app>瞋
<lb n="0866b05" ed="T"/>目視夫，應拒<note n="0866020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝獨【三】</note><note n="0866020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猶【大】，獨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866020"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">獨</rdg></app>罵。二者、不一心向夫婿，但
<lb n="0866b06" ed="T"/>念他男子。三者、欲令夫死早得更嫁，是為三
<lb n="0866b07" ed="T"/>惡。」玉耶默然無辭答佛。</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866b0710" rend="inline">佛告玉耶：「世間<note n="0866021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（復）＋有【三】</note><note n="0866021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，復有【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866021"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">復有</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866b08" ed="T"/>七輩<note n="0866022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婦＋（何等為七輩）【三】</note><note n="0866022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婦【大】，婦何等為七輩【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866022"><lem wit="【大】">婦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婦何等為七輩</rdg></app>：一、婦如母，二、婦如妹，三、婦如善知
<lb n="0866b09" ed="T"/>識，四、婦如婦，五、婦如婢，六、婦如怨家，七、婦如
<lb n="0866b10" ed="T"/>奪命，是為七輩婦，汝豈<note n="0866023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解＝能【宋】</note><note n="0866023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">解【大】，能【宋】</note><app n="0866023"><lem wit="【大】">解</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">能</rdg></app>乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866b1012" rend="inline">玉耶白佛：「不
<lb n="0866b11" ed="T"/>知七婦盡何所施行？願佛為解之。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866b1114" rend="inline">佛告玉耶：
<lb n="0866b12" ed="T"/>「諦聽諦聽，善思念之，吾當為汝分別解說。何
<lb n="0866b13" ed="T"/>等為母婦？母婦者，愛念夫婿猶若慈母，侍其
<lb n="0866b14" ed="T"/>晨夜不離左右，供養盡心不失時宜，夫若行
<lb n="0866b15" ed="T"/>來恐人輕易，見則憐念心<note n="0866024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【三】</note><note n="0866024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866024"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無</rdg></app>疲厭，憐夫如
<lb n="0866b16" ed="T"/><note n="0866025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝母【宋】</note><note n="0866025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子【大】，母【宋】</note><app n="0866025"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">母</rdg></app>，是為母婦。何等為妹婦？妹婦者，承事夫
<lb n="0866b17" ed="T"/>婿盡其敬誠，若如兄弟同氣分形，骨肉至親
<lb n="0866b18" ed="T"/>無有二情，尊奉敬之如妹事兄，是為妹婦。何
<lb n="0866b19" ed="T"/>等為善知識婦者？侍其夫婿愛念懇至，依依
<lb n="0866b20" ed="T"/>戀戀不能相棄，私密之事常相告示，見過依
<lb n="0866b21" ed="T"/>呵令行無失，善事相<note n="0866026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬＝教【三】</note><note n="0866026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敬【大】，教【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866026"><lem wit="【大】">敬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">教</rdg></app>使益明慧，<note n="0866027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（相親）＋相【三】</note><note n="0866027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，相親相【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866027"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">相親相</rdg></app>愛欲
<lb n="0866b22" ed="T"/>令度世如善知識，是為善知識婦。何等為婦
<lb n="0866b23" ed="T"/>婦者？供養大人竭誠盡敬，承事夫婿謙遜順
<lb n="0866b24" ed="T"/>命，夙興夜寐恭恪言<note n="0866028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝令【三】</note><note n="0866028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命【大】，令【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866028"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">令</rdg></app>，口無逸言身無逸行，
<lb n="0866b25" ed="T"/>有善推讓過則稱己，誨訓仁施勸進為道，心
<lb n="0866b26" ed="T"/>端<note n="0866029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">專＝意【三】</note><note n="0866029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">專【大】，意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866029"><lem wit="【大】">專</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">意</rdg></app>一無有<note n="0866030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">分邪精＝邪䀎直【三】</note><note n="0866030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">分邪精【大】，邪䀎直【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866030"><lem wit="【大】">分邪，精</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">邪䀎直</rdg></app>修婦節終無闕廢，進
<lb n="0866b27" ed="T"/>不犯儀退不失禮，唯和為貴，是為婦婦。何等
<lb n="0866b28" ed="T"/>為婢婦者？常懷畏慎不敢自慢，兢兢趣事無
<lb n="0866b29" ed="T"/>所避憚，心常<note n="0866031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恭恪＝謙恭【三】</note><note n="0866031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恭恪【大】，謙恭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866031"><lem wit="【大】">恭恪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">謙恭</rdg></app>忠孝盡節，言以柔軟性常
<pb n="0866c" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0143.0866c"/>
<lb n="0866c01" ed="T"/>和穆，口不犯麁邪之<note n="0866032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝語【三】</note><note n="0866032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，語【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866032"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">語</rdg></app>，身不入放逸之行，
<lb n="0866c02" ed="T"/>貞良純一質朴直信，恒自嚴整，以禮自將，夫
<lb n="0866c03" ed="T"/>婿納幸不以憍慢，設不接遇不以為怨，或得
<lb n="0866c04" ed="T"/>捶杖分受不恚，及見罵辱默而不恨，甘心樂
<lb n="0866c05" ed="T"/>受無有二意，勸進所好不妬聲色，遇己曲薄
<lb n="0866c06" ed="T"/>不訴求直，務修婦節不擇衣食，專精恭恪唯
<lb n="0866c07" ed="T"/>恐不及，<note n="0866033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬奉＝奉敬【三】</note><note n="0866033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敬奉【大】，奉敬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866033"><lem wit="【大】">敬奉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">奉敬</rdg></app>夫婿<note n="0866034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋婢【三】</note><note n="0866034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婢【大】，如婢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866034"><lem wit="【大】">婢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">如婢</rdg></app>事大家，是為婢婦。何
<lb n="0866c08" ed="T"/>等為怨家婦者？見夫不歡恒懷瞋恚，晝夜思
<lb n="0866c09" ed="T"/>念欲得解離，<note n="0866035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝雖為【三】</note><note n="0866035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，雖為【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866035"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">雖為</rdg></app>夫婦心常如寄客，狺狺鬪諍
<lb n="0866c10" ed="T"/>無所畏<note n="0866036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忌＝避【三】</note><note n="0866036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忌【大】，避【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866036"><lem wit="【大】">忌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">避</rdg></app>，亂頭墜臥不<note n="0866037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可＝肯【三】</note><note n="0866037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">可【大】，肯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866037"><lem wit="【大】">可</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">肯</rdg></app>作使，不念治家
<lb n="0866c11" ed="T"/>養活兒子，或行婬蕩不知羞恥，<note n="0866038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狀如＝如狀【三】＊</note><note n="0866038" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->狀如【大】＊，如狀【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0866038"><lem wit="【大】">狀如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">如狀</rdg></app>犬畜毀
<lb n="0866c12" ed="T"/>辱親<note n="0866039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">里＝理【宋】＊</note><note n="0866039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">里【大】＊，理【宋】＊</note><app n="0866039"><lem wit="【大】">里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">理</rdg></app>，譬如怨家，是為怨家婦。何等為奪
<lb n="0866c13" ed="T"/>命婦者？晝夜不寐<note n="0866040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恚＝毒【三】</note><note n="0866040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恚【大】，毒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866040"><lem wit="【大】">恚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">毒</rdg></app>心相向，當何方便得
<lb n="0866c14" ed="T"/>相遠離？欲與毒藥恐人覺知，或至親<app type="star" corresp="#0866039"><lem wit="【大】">里</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">理</rdg></app>遠
<lb n="0866c15" ed="T"/>近寄之，作<note n="0866041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝使【三】</note><note n="0866041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，使【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866041"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">使</rdg></app>瞋恚常共賊之，若持寶物雇人
<lb n="0866c16" ed="T"/>害之，或使傍<note n="0866042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝人【三】</note><note n="0866042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夫【大】，人【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866042"><lem wit="【大】">夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">人</rdg></app>伺而殺之，怨抂夫命，是為
<lb n="0866c17" ed="T"/>奪命婦。是為七輩婦。」玉耶默然。</p>
<lb n="0866c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0866c1801">佛告玉耶：「五善婦者常有顯名，言行有法眾
<lb n="0866c19" ed="T"/>人愛敬，宗親九族並蒙其榮，天龍鬼神皆來
<lb n="0866c20" ed="T"/>擁護使不抂<note n="0866c2001" resp="CBETA" type="add">撗【CB】【麗-CB】，擴【大】</note><app n="0866c2001"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">撗<note type="cf1">K19n0771_p0796c15</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">擴</rdg></app>，萬分之後得生天上七寶宮
<lb n="0866c21" ed="T"/>殿，在所自然侍從左右，壽命延長恣意所<note n="0866043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝之【三】</note><note n="0866043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲【大】，之【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866043"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866c22" ed="T"/>快樂難言。天上壽盡下生世間，當為富貴<note n="0866044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侯王＝王侯【三】</note><note n="0866044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侯王【大】，王侯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866044"><lem wit="【大】">侯
<lb n="0866c23" ed="T"/>王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">王侯</rdg></app>子孫，端正聰慧人所奉尊。其<note n="0866045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝二【三】</note><note n="0866045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡【大】，二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866045"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">二</rdg></app>婦者常得
<lb n="0866c24" ed="T"/>惡名，令現在身不得安寧，數為惡鬼眾毒所
<lb n="0866c25" ed="T"/>病，<note n="0866046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臥起＝起臥【宋】【元】</note><note n="0866046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臥起【大】，起臥【宋】【元】</note><app n="0866046"><lem wit="【大】">臥起</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">起臥</rdg></app>不安惡夢驚怖，所願不得多逢災
<lb n="0866c26" ed="T"/>撗，萬分之後魂<note n="0866047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝魄【三】</note><note n="0866047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神【大】，魄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866047"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">魄</rdg></app>受形，當入地獄餓鬼畜
<lb n="0866c27" ed="T"/>生，展轉三塗累劫不竟。」</p>
<lb n="0866c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0866c2801">佛告玉耶：「是七輩婦汝欲<note n="0866048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行何＝何行【三】</note><note n="0866048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行何【大】，何行【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866048"><lem wit="【大】">行何</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">何行</rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0866c2813" rend="inline">玉耶流涕前
<lb n="0866c29" ed="T"/>白佛言：「我心愚癡無智所作，自今<note n="0866049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【明】</note><note n="0866049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，已【明】</note><app n="0866049"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">已</rdg></app>後改往
<pb n="0867a" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0143.0867a"/>
<lb n="0867a01" ed="T"/>修來，當如婢婦，奉事<app type="star" corresp="#0865005"><lem wit="【大】">妐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">公</rdg></app>姑夫婿，盡我壽命不
<lb n="0867a02" ed="T"/>敢憍慢。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0867a0204" rend="inline">佛告玉耶：「善哉！善哉！人誰無<note n="0867001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＋（過）【三】</note><note n="0867001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過【大】，過過【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867001"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">過過</rdg></app>？能
<lb n="0867a03" ed="T"/>改者，善莫大焉。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0867a0307" rend="inline">玉耶即前請受十戒為優婆
<lb n="0867a04" ed="T"/>夷。佛告玉耶：「持<note n="0867002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一戒＝戒一【三】</note><note n="0867002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一戒【大】，戒一【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867002"><lem wit="【大】">一戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">戒一</rdg></app>者、不得殺生，二者、不
<lb n="0867a05" ed="T"/>得偷盜取他人<note n="0867003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔財〕－【三】</note><note n="0867003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">財【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867003"><lem wit="【大】">財</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>物，三者、不得<note n="0867004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬＋（妷犯）【宋】＋（泆犯）【元】【明】</note><note n="0867004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬【大】，婬妷犯【宋】，婬泆犯【元】【明】</note><app n="0867004"><lem wit="【大】">婬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">婬妷犯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">婬泆犯</rdg></app>他男子，
<lb n="0867a06" ed="T"/>四者、不得<note n="0867005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲酒＝兩舌【三】</note><note n="0867005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲酒【大】，兩舌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867005"><lem wit="【大】">飲酒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">兩舌</rdg></app>，五者、不得<note n="0867006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄語＝飲酒【三】</note><note n="0867006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妄語【大】，飲酒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867006"><lem wit="【大】">妄語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">飲酒</rdg></app>，六者、不得
<lb n="0867a07" ed="T"/>惡罵，七者、不得綺語，八者、不得嫉妬，九者、不
<lb n="0867a08" ed="T"/>得瞋恚，十者、<note n="0867007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當信作＝信【三】</note><note n="0867007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當信作【大】，信【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867007"><lem wit="【大】">當信作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">信</rdg></app>善得福作惡得罪。信佛
<lb n="0867a09" ed="T"/>信法信比丘僧，是為十戒優婆夷法，終身奉
<lb n="0867a10" ed="T"/>行不敢違犯。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0867a1006" rend="inline">佛說經已，諸弟子皆<note n="0867008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悉〕－【三】</note><note n="0867008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867008"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作禮。
<lb n="0867a11" ed="T"/>給孤長者<app type="star" corresp="#0866015"><lem wit="【大】">姑妐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">公姑</rdg></app>大小及<note n="0867009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】</note><note n="0867009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867009"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>玉耶，盡行澡水
<lb n="0867a12" ed="T"/>供養佛百味<note n="0867010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【宋】【元】</note><note n="0867010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲【大】，飯【宋】【元】</note><app n="0867010"><lem wit="【大】">飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">飯</rdg></app>食。佛告玉耶：「當信布施常得
<lb n="0867a13" ed="T"/>其福<note n="0867011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔德〕－【三】</note><note n="0867011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867011"><lem wit="【大】">德</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，後世當復生長者家。」玉耶言：「諾。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0867a1316" rend="inline">佛
<lb n="0867a14" ed="T"/>飯畢<note n="0867012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竟噠＝訖達【三】</note><note n="0867012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竟噠【大】，訖達【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867012"><lem wit="【大】">竟，噠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">訖達</rdg></app>嚫呪願：「五十善神擁護汝身。」佛
<lb n="0867a15" ed="T"/>告玉<note n="0867013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＋（言）【三】</note><note n="0867013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，耶言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867013"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耶言</rdg></app>：「勤念經戒。」玉耶言：「我蒙佛恩得聞
<lb n="0867a16" ed="T"/>經法。」皆前為佛作禮而<note n="0867014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">退＝去【三】</note><note n="0867014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">退【大】，去【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867014"><lem wit="【大】">退</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">去</rdg></app>。</p>
